    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but a \"drastic change\" or a doctor doesnt change the fact that the core of everything feels broken. it feels like i've tried every single way to fix it and nothing works. when you say letting go is an \"understandable impulse\"... do you mean like, it's actually a rational thing to consider when things are this bad?",
